Enum RequestStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<RequestStatus>
      • com.kamontat.constant.RequestStatus
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public enum RequestStatus
extends java.lang.Enum<RequestStatus>
    when this program need to request some thing in the internet
    this might return some exception or code that program can't handle by itself so this class will have develop and user to know that which exception be happen and what best result that we should handle
    mostly this enum class will use with RequestException to handle exception easier.
